NG0542:2: tan+t+ra ra dza ma ha ma ya ga r+b+ha ku la na ma //
NG0542:4: rgyud kyi rgyal po chen po sgyu 'phrul snying po bkod pa zhes bya ba //
NG0542:5: bcom ldan 'das zhi khro rang snang gi lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0542:6: 'di skad bdag gi bshad pa'i dus gcig na //
NG0542:7: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang *//
NG0542:10: yon tan 'phrin las su lhun gyis grub pa'i ye shes //
NG0542:11: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi mnga' bdag / dpal kun tu bzang po rang snang ba'i sku //
NG0542:13: zhal gsum du snang ba rdo rje dang *//
NG0542:15: rin po che g.yas na 'dzin pa //
NG0542:19: rdo rje skyil mo krung gi kun tu bzang mo
NG0542:20: dang 'du 'bral med pa de nyid kyi khyad par
NG0542:21: las // rdo rje 'chang rin po che 'byung ba dang *//
NG0542:31: gzhan yang sa'i snying po dang *//
NG0542:47: gzhan yang thub pa chen po srid thub 'dzin dang //
NG0542:48: thub pa chen po rnam par rgyal ba dang *//
NG0542:51: rnam par snang byed dang chos kyi rgyal po dang gzhan yang stobs po che dang *//
NG0542:59: de lta bu 'khor dang bcas par gnas so //
NG0542:60: de dag kyang bde stong dbyer med pa'i gnas //
NG0542:61: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin 'phrin las lhun gyi grub pa'i gnas na /
NG0542:62: 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa mi 'gog par gnas pa'i tshe na //
NG0542:63: nam mkha' las chos nyid kyi sgra de yongs su grag go //
NG0542:64: ma rig rmongs pa sgron mes gsal ba'i phyir //
NG0542:65: gnas lugs rang bzhin zhi khro dang *//
NG0542:66: gdul bya sbrul pa'i zhi khro dang *//
NG0542:67: phung po rang rgyud zhi khro dang *//
NG0542:68: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i bdag nyid rnams //
NG0542:69: thabs la mkhas pas gsung du gsol //
NG0542:71: de'i tshe bcom ldan 'das de nyid zhal bzhad pa 'od zer las //
NG0542:72: stod pa nyid kyi glu 'di grag go //
NG0542:73: gnas med gnas la 'od gsal ba //
NG0542:75: bya byed med pa'i sku snang ba //
NG0542:76: sgyu ma'i mig 'khrul rnam par snang *//
NG0542:77: zag bcas gdos pa'i khung po yang *//
NG0542:78: ma skyes snyingapo chos kyi sku //
NG0542:79: byung bgrod gnas par gang snang ba //
NG0542:80: 'bras bu nyid du nges pa'i lam //
NG0542:82: sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i snying po bkod pa las //
NG0542:83: rgyu dang rkyen gyi le'u ste dang po'o // //
NG0542:84: de nas bcom ldan 'das gnas lugs rang bzhin gyi
NG0542:85: ting nge 'dzin la zhugs te 'di gsungs so //
NG0542:86: chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang ni //
NG0542:87: stong nyid rnam dag chos kyi dbyings //
NG0542:88: bem stong dngos bral gdol ba dag //
NG0542:89: rang gi ye shes rang gdangs la //
NG0542:90: 'od gsal stong pa rnam dag gsal //
NG0542:91: bde stong kun 'byung zag pa med //
NG0542:94: ma bcos sprol bral byang chub sems //
NG0542:95: rig stong mtha' brgyad spros dang bral //
NG0542:96: stong gsal pad+ma skyon bral dang *//
NG0542:97: stong nyid snying rje'i snying po can //
NG0542:98: snang stong rdo rje chos kyi sku //
NG0542:99: skye med dam brj-id rnam par ldan //
NG0542:100: stong nyid ma bcos chos kyi sku //
NG0542:101: mtshan dang dpe byad longs spyod rdzogs //
NG0542:102: dngos po snang spyod mngon byang chub //
NG0542:103: snang stong dbyer med rdo rje rgya //
NG0542:104: ma spangs gang mos de 'dul sku //
NG0542:105: ma skyes skye med de bzhin ngang *//
NG0542:106: dgongs pas snang ba brda dang mjal //
NG0542:107: rig ma sgyu mas go par byed //
NG0542:108: grag stong dbyer med brag cha 'dra //
NG0542:109: kun la tshig tshogs rnam par snang *//
NG0542:110: gsal la rtog med don rig cing *//
NG0542:111: 'byed med shes rab mnyam par gnas //
NG0542:112: bdag med dngos po so sor gsal //
NG0542:113: bya ba gang yin mngon du grub //
NG0542:114: nam mkha' lta bu rab tu rtogs //
NG0542:115: rgya dang bral ba'i zhing khams dang *//
NG0542:116: spyod yul dpag dka'i gzhal yas dang *//
NG0542:117: sna tshogs ma spangs ngang gi brgyan //
NG0542:118: lnga btsegs rang snang dag pa'i gdan //
NG0542:119: 'od zer phung po blta na sdug / zhi 'gyur dbyings nas phyag rgya 'bar //
NG0542:120: kun tu ma lus yongs su gang *//
NG0542:121: 'dod pa'i bsam pa kun dang mjal //
NG0542:122: mun pa drag pos gnod pa bral //
NG0542:123: zhi rgyas dbang drag lhun grub gnas //
NG0542:124: me long nang nas rdo rje rigs //
NG0542:125: zhe sdang can la khro bar gsal //
NG0542:126: mnyam nyid dang gnas pad+ma'i rigs //
NG0542:127: nga rgya 'dzoms mdzad zhi gnas chu //
NG0542:128: sor rtog ngang nas pad+ma'i rigs //
NG0542:129: 'dod chags sreg pa'i lhag mthong me //
NG0542:130: byang chub ngang gnas las kyi rigs //
NG0542:132: chos dbyings ngang gnas de bzhin rigs //
NG0542:133: ma rigs mun sel dar rgud stongs //
NG0542:134: ye shes lnga yi rigs 'dzin pa //
NG0542:135: sangs rgyas lnga yi gdung du gsal //
NG0542:136: nyon mongs lnga yi zhi sbyong ba //
NG0542:137: he ru ka yi phyag rgyar gsal //
NG0542:138: chos sku skye med snying po ru //
NG0542:139: rang bzhin zhi khro lhun gyis grub //
NG0542:140: dper na nyungs kar mar khyab 'dra //
NG0542:141: til gang lta bu gang gnas pa //
NG0542:142: gang gi gang mthong dar snang ba //
NG0542:143: snang gsal nam mkha' shar ba la //
NG0542:144: re re zhing la re re snang *//
NG0542:145: gcig las tha dad snang bar zad //
NG0542:146: 'byung rgyu lin par der snang ngo //
NG0542:148: chos thams cad rang bzhin gnas lugs kyi zhi khro gsal bar 'gyur to //
NG0542:149: sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i snying po bkod pa las //
NG0542:150: gzhi dang rang bzhin gyi le'u ste gnyis pa'o //
NG0542:151: // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis gdul bya la
NG0542:152: snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te
NG0542:153: 'di gsungs so // rnam dag phung po lnga 'chang ba //
NG0542:154: zag bcas rgyu la 'bras bu gnas //
NG0542:155: mi bskyodardo rje'i phyag rgya ni //
NG0542:156: yul la spyod pas sangs rgyas mig //
NG0542:157: sa snying sgeg mo rdo rje bran //
NG0542:158: kun bzang me tog mthing ka'i r-igs //
NG0542:161: zhe sdang khong khro'i thub pa gnyis //
NG0542:162: rang gi gdangs la rigs su grub //
NG0542:163: yon tan rin chen ma ma ki //
NG0542:164: nam mkha'i snying po 'phreng ba ma //
NG0542:165: kun bzang spos me stobs po che //
NG0542:166: zhags pa 'ching mdzad nga rgyal rigs *//
NG0542:167: yi dwags 'dul byed gser gyi mdog //
NG0542:168: snang ba gos dkar spyan ras gzigs //
NG0542:169: glu ma 'jam dpal mar me ma //
NG0542:170: sha kya seng ge rang gi rigs //
NG0542:171: le brgan pad+ma ra ga can //
NG0542:172: don grub dam tshig sgron ma che //
NG0542:173: phyag na rdo rje gar mkhan ma //
NG0542:174: sgrib pa rnams sel dri chab ma //
NG0542:175: phrag dog can las ljang khu 'phro //
NG0542:176: snang mdzad dbyings ma gti mug 'dul *//
NG0542:177: kun bzang yid chos dkar gsal zhing *//
NG0542:178: kun la rigs bdag mi 'gyur mdog *//
NG0542:179: dbang po rnam shes yul dang bcas //
NG0542:180: bzhi bcu tsa gnyis ngo bo ni //
NG0542:181: rdo rje 'khor lo rin po che //
NG0542:183: rin chen myu gu ral gri 'bar //
NG0542:186: pi wang gar bsgyur dung du gsal //
NG0542:187: mun nang klung shing po ti chos //
NG0542:189: spos dang me tog mar me dri //
NG0542:190: thod dbyug rdo rje thod sbrul 'dzin //
NG0542:191: rgya gram ban d+ha lca kyu zhags //
NG0542:192: lcags sgrogs dril bu las bzhi rgya //
NG0542:193: pi wang sreg pas go mtshon sgrom //
NG0542:194: me chu po ti mnyam gzhag 'phro //
NG0542:195: tsa btsegs gsum dang gnyis rkyang pa //
NG0542:196: snang ba phye na snang ba ste //
NG0542:197: dud dang ku mu nyi zla 'dra //
NG0542:198: bai du r+ya dang kar ka ri //
NG0542:199: le brgan gser sbyangs in+ta ni //
NG0542:200: gnyis las gnyis 'dzin drug na drug / rigs las mi 'da' chaul par 'dzin //
NG0542:202: ma skyes ma 'gags yul mtshon pa //
NG0542:203: mtshan ma nye bar brtags pa dang *//
NG0542:204: zin mdzad mi bskyod 'dul dbang phyir //
NG0542:205: mtha' yas tha dad dam par 'brel //
NG0542:206: las su 'brel bas dgongs pa dang *//
NG0542:208: skyil klung rang bzhin dang du gnas //
NG0542:209: babs bzhon bzhengs thabs dor thabs bgrad //
NG0542:211: lhun sdug gzi brjid 'bar ba dang *//
NG0542:212: sku dang gsung thugs yon tan las //
NG0542:213: mtshan dang dpe byad sprad kyis brgyan //
NG0542:214: ting 'dzin tsol bas gang dag pa //
NG0542:215: rtog pa las mtha' lta ba dang *//
NG0542:217: chos nyid rnam par 'byed pa dang *//
NG0542:218: dga' ba shin tu sbyang ba dang *//
NG0542:219: ting 'dzin dran pa btang snyoms dang *//
NG0542:220: rtson 'grus mdzes pa'i rgyan dang ldan //
NG0542:221: bzhugs bzhengs gshegs gzigs 'khug pa dang */
NG0542:222: dgongs bstan rten 'byor bdud pa dang *//
NG0542:223: lcam me ma le lhan ne ba //
NG0542:224: sa le zhi ba ngang tshul can //
NG0542:225: phyi nang med par gsal na ngan //
NG0542:226: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor mdzad cing *//
NG0542:227: sa yi khyab par kun bgrod nas //
NG0542:228: yon tan che ba bcom nas gnas //
NG0542:231: 'jig rten drug tu sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud zhi bar snang ngo //
NG0542:232: sgyu 'phrul drwa ba snying po bkod pa las //
NG0542:233: chos nyid bzhi ba'i le'u ste gsum pa'o // //
NG0542:234: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis drag po rtogs 'joms
NG0542:235: kyi ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te 'di
NG0542:236: gsungs so // 'dzin pa'i dbang gis sdug bsngal zhing *//
NG0542:237: gdug pa srid gsum 'dul ba la //
NG0542:238: nga rgyal chen po bstan pa'i phyir //
NG0542:239: sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i khro bo snang *//
NG0542:240: rdo rje khros pa khrag 'thung mthing *//
NG0542:242: dkar dmar zhal du nyon mongs 'dren //
NG0542:243: tse dgu tse lnga sti ra dang *//
NG0542:245: shes rab 'khyud pas chags pa stobs //
NG0542:247: dkar ser smug nag gti mug 'dren //
NG0542:248: 'khor lo rdo rje sta ri dang *//
NG0542:249: dril bu dung dmar tri shul 'chang *//
NG0542:251: sngo dmar ser nag nga rgyal gsol //
NG0542:252: rin chen rdo rje sti ra dang *//
NG0542:253: dril bu dung dmar dgra sta rol //
NG0542:255: khro mo dbyings phyug nyer gnas pa'i //
NG0542:256: dkar ser dmar nag brjid pa la /
NG0542:257: pad+ma rdo rje sti ra dang *//
NG0542:258: dril bu dung dmar rnge'u chung can /
NG0542:260: dkar dmar ljang nag 'bar ba la //
NG0542:261: rgya gram rdo rje sti ra dang *//
NG0542:262: dril bu dung dmar thong gshel rol //
NG0542:263: stag gzig dom dang ma he dang */
NG0542:264: khyu mchog dregs pa gnon pa'i steng *//
NG0542:265: 'gying stabs mdzes pas tshar gcod mdzad //
NG0542:266: ka ri tse ri bra mo ha //
NG0542:267: pe ta li dang pu ka si //
NG0542:268: ka sma ri dang sman sha ni //
NG0542:269: tsan+da li ste ma mo tsho //
NG0542:270: sngo ser dmar dang nag pa dang *//
NG0542:271: dkar ser ljang khu mthing ka dang *//
NG0542:272: ser skya lus kyi mdog 'dzin cing */
NG0542:273: ban+d+ha byis dbyag mda' gzhur bcas //
NG0542:274: / kha t+wam chu srin rgyal mtshan 'dzin //
NG0542:275: rdo rje bying sha byis rgyus 'dren *//
NG0542:276: dung dmar rdo rje byis snying za //
NG0542:277: mchog gi mgo lus 'brel bar mdzad //
NG0542:278: seng ge wa sbyang rta gdong dam //
NG0542:279: bya rgod dkang ka bya rog dang *//
NG0542:281: dkar dmar ser ljang mthing ka dang *//
NG0542:282: sna tshogs lus su gnas pa ste //
NG0542:283: kha na ro 'dzin zhing gnas blta //
NG0542:284: byis pa'i khong bldag gri khug 'bral //
NG0542:285: zangs gri ban+d+ha dmar gyi bkang *//
NG0542:286: zhing khrag khur ba nar skye'i mdog //
NG0542:287: kha na ro thogs ban+d+ha gri //
NG0542:289: rta yi mgo can lcags kyu dkar //
NG0542:290: phag gi gdong pa zhags pa bser //
NG0542:291: sbre gdong lcags sgrog dmar mo dred //
NG0542:292: sbyang gdong dril bu ljang nag khro //
NG0542:293: kun kyang zhing gi gdan la bzhugs //
NG0542:294: slas dang byin mo bran mo rnams //
NG0542:295: srin mo tshangs ma lha chen mo //
NG0542:296: gtogs 'dod gzhon nu rgya byin ma //
NG0542:297: rdo rje bdud tsi zla ba mo //
NG0542:298: pe cin sin mo za byed ma //
NG0542:301: 'dod pa nor bsrung rlung lha mo //
NG0542:302: gsod byed me mo phag mo dang *//
NG0542:303: rgan byed sna chad chu lha mo //
NG0542:304: nag mo ser mo dmar ljang mo //
NG0542:305: phyi yi mkha' 'gro rang rgyud ma //
NG0542:306: nang gi mkha' 'gro rang rgyud ston //
NG0542:307: gsang ba'i sbrul pa mgo brnyan ma //
NG0542:308: bka' rtags rdo rje rang rtags 'chang *//
NG0542:309: zhing kyang rang gi gdan la bzhugs //
NG0542:310: dpal gyi pham phabs lhag ma len //
NG0542:311: gdug pas phye nas snang ba'o //
NG0542:312: ri bo rgya bcu tsa gcig dag / snang bar ston pa bdag nyid ni //
NG0542:313: ming mtshan brda dang tha snyad dang *//
NG0542:314: yod med the tsom nges pa 'jog *//
NG0542:316: sbyor zhen dngos gzhi skyed pa dang *//
NG0542:317: rkyen las mtshan ma mngon pa dang *//
NG0542:318: sbyor pa rtags kyi mtshan ma bcu //
NG0542:319: mi rtogs ma rmongs mo 'gog pas //
NG0542:320: zhi gnas lhag mthong zung du 'brel //
NG0542:321: mi dmigs ma grub ma skyes pas //
NG0542:322: gzhi lam 'bras bu rang sar gnas //
NG0542:323: dgu spyod rang bzhin gcig pa yis //
NG0542:324: khro ba drag shul dam rdzas len //
NG0542:325: gang dang gang las gang phyir gang *//
NG0542:326: ngang shug bcas dang bcos par 'gyur //
NG0542:327: yul gnas las dang 'bras bu dang *//
NG0542:328: rgyu dang 'bras bu dang phyir 'gyur bas //
NG0542:330: rdzings bshig za dang stobs pa dang *//
NG0542:331: sdud dang bde dang snang ba dang *//
NG0542:332: mtha' yas thogs med mi bskyod las //
NG0542:333: mi 'da' rol pa che ba ni //
NG0542:334: gdul bya rang bzhin shes rab thabs //
NG0542:335: thams cad thugs rje dam pa dang *//
NG0542:336: 'phrin las ye shes chos nyid dgongs //
NG0542:337: grub pa dang ni mdzad pa ste //
NG0542:338: ma skyes ma rmongs mi g.yo ba //
NG0542:339: ma 'gag ma chags ma bcings dang *//
NG0542:340: mi bskyod pa dang mi thogs pa //
NG0542:342: gdul bya gzigs dang sprul pa 'gyed //
NG0542:343: ci gsol gsan dang mgon skyabs dang *//
NG0542:344: dug chen zad dang thig chen ston //
NG0542:345: skye zhing gcod dang rgyu drug 'don //
NG0542:346: mtha' drug rdzogs dang las bzhis sgrol //
NG0542:347: gnyen pa 'gran zla med pa dang //
NG0542:348: khyad 'phags che btsan gcig pu dang *//
NG0542:350: thabs mang ma phab mnga' yang rdzogs //
NG0542:351: kun la rgyal dang yong mi nus //
NG0542:352: sku gsung thugs dang mthu yi rngom //
NG0542:353: ri bo gar thabs khyad 'byung stobs //
NG0542:354: ci ltar snang bas cir yang 'grub //
NG0542:355: zil gyis gnon pas 'tsham rngam tsheg / zhal dang ljags dang tshems dang gsung *//
NG0542:356: gang du rngubs pas cir yang 'gyur //
NG0542:357: yongs su gcod pas go bas sgrogs //
NG0542:358: nam mkha'i skar tshogs rgya mtsho'i rlabs //
NG0542:359: tsi shing nags tshal gar gyi 'phreng *//
NG0542:360: dgongs pas 'phrin las de tshul dang *//
NG0542:361: yon tan sa gzhi thugs rje'i dpe //
NG0542:362: 'byung bdud dur khrod sba bkong pa //
NG0542:363: bla na med pa cir yang 'grub //
NG0542:364: gnas dang gnon pa zhing sbyor kyi /
NG0542:365: khyad par tshul du de ltar snang *//
NG0542:369: nam mkha'i gtos chen nor bu rin chen dang *//
NG0542:371: sku chen yan lag rags pa dang *//
NG0542:372: grangs mang rkyen dang 'tsham pa dang *//
NG0542:373: bkur 'os gtso bor mthong ba dang *//
NG0542:374: khyad zhugs yid dang 'thad pa dang *//
NG0542:375: gdangs chen stong gsum gang ba dang *//
NG0542:376: tshig myur the tsom gcod pa dang *//
NG0542:377: don dam nye tsher gcod pa dang */
NG0542:378: khyad par yon tan mthong ba dang */
NG0542:379: yang la re dogs med pa dang *//
NG0542:380: gsal bas mtha' gnyis spangs pa dang *//
NG0542:381: thugs rje thugs dam rdzogs pa dang *//
NG0542:382: ma smos thabs kyisa'adul ba dang *//
NG0542:383: med pa zad mi shes pa dang *//
NG0542:384: gcig la 'dod dgur ston pa dang *//
NG0542:385: gnod sbyor phan par mdzad pa dang *//
NG0542:386: thabs mkhas skyon gyis ma gos dang *//
NG0542:387: mi snyems nyams bag rol ba dang *//
NG0542:388: 'khor ba yun ring mi snyem dang *//
NG0542:389: mgon skyabs rgyun du mdzad pa dang *//
NG0542:390: dgongs don lhun gyi grub pa dang *//
NG0542:391: chos rgyal snyems pa mi mnga' dang *//
NG0542:392: nyams bag chen po rol pa dang *//
NG0542:393: gang gi dpung gis mi snyel dang *//
NG0542:394: yun gyi don srid snyems pa dang *//
NG0542:395: stobs kyis gzhan gang gnon pa dang *//
NG0542:396: rdzu 'phrul mi gnas bskyed pa dang *//
NG0542:397: ma zid pa yi mdzod mar 'dang *//
NG0542:398: skye bo yo byad mos pa dang *//
NG0542:399: rdzu 'phrul ches dang ye shes dang *//
NG0542:400: sems tsho las dang smon lam dang *//
NG0542:401: mnyam nyid sku dang thugs thigs dang *//
NG0542:404: gshe dang bzhad dang snying rje dang *//
NG0542:405: rngam dang ngo mtshar zhi ba dang *//
NG0542:406: byams pa'i blo dang snying rje'i gros //
NG0542:407: dga' ba'i thabs dang gtang snyoms mod *//
NG0542:408: snying rje chos nyid mi 'byed pa //
NG0542:409: grub pa ma spang ma g.yos pa *//
NG0542:410: smon lam sprul pa mi gtong ba //
NG0542:411: ma chags pa yi stobs rnams rdzogs //
NG0542:412: chos nyid ye shes thugs rje dang *//
NG0542:417: thams cad khro bo'i phyag rgyar gsal lo //
NG0542:418: sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i snying po bkod pa las //
NG0542:419: rtog 'joms khro bo'i le'u ste bzhi pa'o ///
NG0542:420: / de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis rang rgyud yongs
NG0542:421: su dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin la zhugs te 'di
NG0542:422: gsungs so // sems can tsa ba med pa ni //
NG0542:423: skye rgyu med pa'i skye ba can //
NG0542:424: spang la sha mo rdol ba 'dra //
NG0542:425: sgyu ma'i lus po khong steng ni //
NG0542:426: snying po med pa'i pags pa can //
NG0542:428: ma rig rang nas 'byung ba ni //
NG0542:429: me long dag la g.ya' gnas 'dra //
NG0542:430: rnam rtog 'tshol kro byed pa dang *//
NG0542:431: khyi kun khyim du zhugs pa 'dra //
NG0542:432: bag chags snod du sogs pa ni //
NG0542:433: rgyal po bang mdzod kha phye 'dra //
NG0542:434: rkyen ngan 'bras bu ngan pa ni //
NG0542:437: sangs rgyas 'khor bar lhung na ni //
NG0542:438: bya rgod gshog pa chag pa 'dra //
NG0542:439: sems can sangs rgyas rgyur gnas pa //
NG0542:441: rang rig bag chags sgrib pa ni //
NG0542:442: nyi ma sprin gyi khebs pa 'dra //
NG0542:443: rnam rtog rkun bur ldang ba ni //
NG0542:444: nam mkha'i ngang nas sprin byung 'dra //
NG0542:445: 'jig rten brtan g.yo dngos po kun //
NG0542:446: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor chen po ste //
NG0542:448: srid gsum sems can thams cad la /
NG0542:449: srog shing gsum dang 'khor lo bzhi //
NG0542:450: brgyad dang drug tu ldan par gnas //
NG0542:452: la la na dang re sa na //
NG0542:453: / a wa d+hu ti'i mnyam gnas pa //
NG0542:454: dri chu khrag dang dkyus par gnas //
NG0542:455: thabs dang shes rab dbyer med pa' //
NG0542:456: g.yas dang g.yon dang dbus na gnas //
NG0542:457: skyes bu bud med gnyis gnas dang *//
NG0542:458: khug pa kha brgyad har ba ste //
NG0542:459: pad can dung can ri mo can //
NG0542:460: ban glang can dang lcug phran can //
NG0542:461: gdong gcig mi reg 'phyar bar gnas //
NG0542:462: ro ma rkyang ma kun 'dar ma //
NG0542:463: a li ka li mnyam gnas dang *//
NG0542:464: tha dad yod pas dam rdzas rgyu //
NG0542:465: spyi bo mgrin pa snying dkar dang *//
NG0542:467: zhal dang phrad pa gnas pa ni //
NG0542:468: bde ba chen po'i 'khor lo dang *//
NG0542:469: de nyid longs spyod chos dang ni //
NG0542:470: sbrul pa mes dang rlung dang bi //
NG0542:471: steng nas sor dang 'og nas sor //
NG0542:472: kum la dbyangs dang gsal byed khyab //
NG0542:473: 'bru brgyad drug pa sngags kyi mda' //
NG0542:474: a ka tsa ta ta pa ya sha //
NG0542:475: dga' bzhi tshogs pa rnam bzhi tshogs pa yis //
NG0542:479: chos nyid ye shes rang rgyud dang *//
NG0542:480: yon tan bzhi las brgyad du gnas //
NG0542:481: 'od dbyibs tshul dang snying po dang *//
NG0542:482: sa bon yid dang shes par bya //
NG0542:483: chos nyid lhan cig dud 'gro zlum //
NG0542:484: kun bzhi om gyi snying por ldan //
NG0542:485: pu tri dngul chu 'jon mar tsi //
NG0542:486: za 'og gur khyim nang na bkra //
NG0542:487: ye shes lha mo gru bzhi yi //
NG0542:488: a nri hum ni bde chen thugs //
NG0542:489: shes sgo le brgan brgyud pa 'dra //
NG0542:490: yon tan dmyal ba yi dwags am //
NG0542:491: zla khams gsung gi rang bzhin yin //
NG0542:492: dri du nyon mongs yid dang bcas //
NG0542:493: dmigs sgyu tsa skya zil chags pa //
NG0542:494: zang zhun rwa gan tsi song 'dra //
NG0542:495: rang rgyud dmar nag o gshol dbyibs //
NG0542:496: de ni blo dbug smod yin te //
NG0542:497: shes pa gsum la snyoms par 'gebs //
NG0542:498: drag po ljang nag sgo lnga'i rten //
NG0542:499: mdom dud ye shes snying po'i tsa //
NG0542:500: de dbus ye shes snying po'i sku //
NG0542:501: dar skud 'tshal khu gser gyi blangs //
NG0542:502: nyi ma me long ngar dag ni //
NG0542:503: 'byung ba bzhi yi dwangs ma ste //
NG0542:504: bde ba'i dngas ma nam mkha'i khams //
NG0542:505: 'phrin las bzhi dang bsnyen bsgrub bzhi //
NG0542:506: dbu rgyan cod pan 'phreng ba dang *//
NG0542:507: go cha rgyal mtshan phyag rgya dang *//
NG0542:508: gdugs dang bum pa bza' btung dang *//
NG0542:509: snying po lnga yi dbang lnga dang *//
NG0542:510: nyan dang 'chad dang sgom sgrub dang *//
NG0542:511: 'phrin las rdo rje rgyal po dang *//
NG0542:512: gsang ba chen po bde chen po //
NG0542:513: lta ba dang ni sbyor pa dang *//
NG0542:514: sngags dang phyag rgyas mchod pa dang *//
NG0542:515: ting 'dzin rol ba'i rgyur gnas pa //
NG0542:516: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor dkyil 'khor mchog / 'byung ba shes rab rigs kyi yum //
NG0542:517: chen po rigs kyi de bzhin te //
NG0542:518: byang chub sems ni rdo rje tshogs //
NG0542:519: dbang pos yul dus rig pa rnams //
NG0542:520: kun tu bzang po dkyil 'khor la //
NG0542:521: bdag nyid chen po lhag pa yis //
NG0542:522: thugs kyi ye shes lnga lta zhing *//
NG0542:523: ka ra na bcings chos bdun gyis //
NG0542:524: nam mkha'i ba bzhos ye shes ni /
NG0542:525: snying po thig le mnyam sbyor bas //
NG0542:526: bde ba'i ye shes rol mo yis //
NG0542:527: ye shes dgyes dang mchod par dbul //
NG0542:528: zag pa med pa'i bsod nams kyis //
NG0542:529: ye shes sgyu mar rang snang pa //
NG0542:530: rol mo'i dkyil 'khor mtha' yas mchog / 'gro ba zhing 'gyur mtha' yas 'dren //
NG0542:531: 'das pa'i glong nas mun pa mkhyen //
NG0542:532: mun pa'i gling nas 'das pa shes //
NG0542:533: rang rig ye shes gdangs la bzhugs //
NG0542:534: sgyu 'phrul drwa ba'i snying po bkod pa las //
NG0542:535: man ngag dra ba'i le'u ste lnga pa'o ///
NG0542:536: / de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis dgongs pa brda'i ting nge 'dzin la zhugs te 'di gsungs so //
NG0542:537: srid gsum sems can thams cad la //
NG0542:539: srog shing dbang po myong ba dang *//
NG0542:540: za byed kun tu rgyu ba dang *//
NG0542:541: klu dang rul sbal rtsangs pa dang *//
NG0542:542: lha sbyin dang ni gzhu las rgyal //
NG0542:543: tsan+d+ha li ni lus kyi mchog / rdo rje hu~m gi 'dug tshul ni //
NG0542:544: gling bzhi ri rab logs la bsdu //
NG0542:546: rlung gis 'khor lo gtsag cing spos *//
NG0542:547: tsan dmar rgya mtsho'i gting nas gnas //
NG0542:548: me lce ri rab lo gsal spar //
NG0542:549: du ba nam mkha'i dbyings su gnas //
NG0542:550: 'dab ma thal ba bshad lam bor //
NG0542:551: mi gdon 'bar bas mkha' la khyab //
NG0542:552: klad dkar mtsho rlabs srub shing gis //
NG0542:553: rlung dang mkhris pa bad kan sbyar //
NG0542:554: rkyal pa kha bcing li ri bcud //
NG0542:555: log gnon rdo rje mda' gzhu brdeg / pho mo ma ning rlung gnas pa //
NG0542:556: drag po nad kyi gnad gcod pa //
NG0542:557: keng rus 'dzin pa'i lus kyi ni //
NG0542:558: phyi dang nang gi don kun 'dzoms //
NG0542:559: skyug dang sbrug pa'i bcud phur gyis //
NG0542:560: sangs rgyas sems can 'dres par byed //
NG0542:561: om gyis 'khor lo gnas la dbab //
NG0542:562: om gyis gsung gi rol par bya //
NG0542:563: swa ni 'dod pa ster ba'i rgya //
NG0542:564: ha yis mi gnas gnas nas gdon //
NG0542:565: sgyu 'phrul snying po bkod pa las //
NG0542:566: drag po sbar ba'i 'khor lo bstan pa'i le'u ste
NG0542:567: drug pa'o // // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis
NG0542:568: snang ba'i bkod pa'i ting nge 'dzin la bzhugs te
NG0542:569: 'di gsungs so // stong nyid don dam rgyu yi mchog / ma 'gag kun rdzob 'bras bu shar //
NG0542:570: ji snyid skyed pa'i rgyu mchog ni //
NG0542:571: ma skyes rig par rang 'byung sku //
NG0542:572: kun rdzob sna tshogs sgyu ma'i mchog / don dam stong nyid 'bras bu 'byung *//
NG0542:573: dper na til mar khyab pa 'dra //
NG0542:574: ma bcos yongs kyis 'od gsal ba //
NG0542:575: stong nyid bskyed pa'i rgyu mchog ni //
NG0542:576: stong nyid snying po bla na med //
NG0542:577: yid bzhin rin chen phung por gnas //
NG0542:578: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NG0542:579: ma rtog pa dang log par rtog / phyogs rtog yang dag nyid ma rtogs //
NG0542:580: 'dul ba dgongs pa gsang ba dang *//
NG0542:581: rang bzhin gsang ba'i don rnams ni //
NG0542:582: lnga dang gnyis dang gcig la bgrod //
NG0542:583: gsum gyi spyod yul shes par bya //
NG0542:584: de shes na ni ye shes te //
NG0542:585: phyogs bcu dus bzhi mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NG0542:586: sku gsung yon tan 'phrin las thugs //
NG0542:587: ma lus bdag nyid zhal mthong ba //
NG0542:588: dbang bskur mchog gi dam pa yin //
NG0542:590: rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor lhun gyis grub //
NG0542:591: rgyan du dkyil 'khor ma lus thogs //
NG0542:592: rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor mnyam sbyor bas //
NG0542:593: thugs rje'i byin rlabs yongs kyi 'byung *//
NG0542:595: sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor sgrol ba yis //
NG0542:596: bya byed med pa dkyil 'khor spyod //
NG0542:597: sgyu 'phrul snying po bkod pa las //
NG0542:598: gzhi lam 'bras bur bsdus pa ste le'u bdun pa'o //
NG0542:599: de nas 'khor thams cad dgyes te bstod pa //
NG0542:600: e ma'o 'dren pa mchog la dga' //
NG0542:601: stong gsal chen po'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0542:602: rnam dag ye shes thugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0542:603: grag stong chos kyi gdung la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0542:604: snang ba dngos med gzugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0542:605: gnyen gsal mnyam pa'i dbyings la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0542:606: don yod gnas pa'i don la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0542:607: zhes brjod pas nyid la nyid dgyes te //
NG0542:608: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mnyam pa chen po
NG0542:609: chos dbyings ni 'gyur ba med pas smra bsam las
NG0542:610: grol te // rdzu 'phrul snying po bkod pa las //
NG0542:611: bstod pas mnyes pa chen po ste le'u brgyad pa'o //
